・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・・

Contact the leadership by using the !contact command. This can only be done by private messaging the bot, @Rubybot.

Use this for submitting complaints, private suggestions, requests for new ranks that you qualify for, request for specific rights (such as perceptor placing rights), or anything else you wish to contact us privately about :hypers: 

*the message will be sent to a private channel visible only to @Owner, @Leader, @SiC, @Trustee, and @Protector.*

